Positive feedback from ClinicRx praising platform as 'work of art' validates product quality.

original_metrics.poll_question: What's holding your pharmacy back from expanding services?
original_metrics.notes: Organic post. Poll results reveal time & staffing shortages (47%) as primary barrier to service expansion, validating messaging around time-saving and efficiency benefits. Limited participation (15 votes) suggests polls may need more active promotion. Results influence future content strategy toward service enablement messaging.

Post boosted from 2025-02-12 to 2025-02-13. Exceptional performance: 63.7% engagement rate, 62.4% CTR. High signal asset — NHS alignment + future-facing innovation. Social proof from NHS leadership (comments from Ghulam Haydar, Wasim Baqir) boosted confidence and credibility. Strong engagement from policy / tech stakeholders vs typical pharmacist-only audience.

original_metrics.poll_question: What's your pharmacy's top priority this year?
original_metrics.notes: Organic poll. Results validate private services growth narrative with 73% voting for expanding private services. High click rate (4.0% CTR) indicates strong interest. Limited reach due to algorithmic throttling of polls compared to other content types.
